GO TO-U Network Charging Stations:
Connector 1&2 : 120kW
Connector 3&4 : 120kW
- balanced charging - will split 60kW per nozzle if 2 cars are charging at the same time.

By Rekascape's entrance, there is also a GO TO-U EV Lifestyle Hub where users can have a seat, relax and enjoy coffee/tea/snacks from our vending machines. 
(Open 8AM - 5PM on Weekdays ONLY)

If you'd like to chat, you can drop by our office next to the GO TO-U EV Lifestyle Hub.
